Package: foolsboard
Version: @VERSION@
Section: web
Priority: optional
Architecture: @ARCH@
Depends: python3 (>= 3.11), python3-venv, ffmpeg, adduser
Maintainer: Victor <vich.martins@gmail.com>
Homepage: https://foolsboard.home
Description: foolsboard -- branching-storyline storyboard app
 A FastAPI + React storyboard with real-time multi-user collaboration. Runs a
 self-contained uvicorn service (single worker) that serves the SPA, API,
 WebSocket, and media on port 9534 -- no web server required. Backed by SQLite
 by default; DATABASE_URL is overridable for Postgres without code changes.
 Can optionally be placed behind a reverse proxy (see the nginx example in
 /usr/share/doc/foolsboard/).
